{"tid":98093,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"黑色沙漠 百人公會《攻略組》招同盟 新血","createTime":"2017-01-28T06:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T14:06:40.000Z","uid":16666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ac774165dd0e2ff9a0d780da03d72a43e66a213","tid":98093,"uid":16666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:55:46.000Z","msg":"團結連登力量<br />\n<br />\n黑沙百人公會《攻略組》尋求同盟 一齊對抗台仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黎緊我地仲會開新既分公會。會一齊做公會任打世界boss，攻城據點戰。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲內有咩唔明都可以盡量問 有唔少高手會解答<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日比三個台仔公會宣戰<br />\n<br />\n3個公會打1個，我地戰績都可以keep到win一半以上<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/145145_14369e5157147e67f78c0a2166acb3f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F145145_14369e5157147e67f78c0a2166acb3f9.jpg&h=f75529b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pzJt414.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpzJt414.jpg&h=f200c88b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有玩緊既香港其他公會 大大小小都好 ，搵埋我地一齊組個同盟 ， 比人打一定會幫你出頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無公會又想搵個公會既，都可以搵埋我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好輸得比d台灣仔<br />\n<br />\n有興趣係game入面add 我<br />\n<br />\n家名：與敵同行<br />\n角色名：Dumbledore<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5W4O5N1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5W4O5N1.jpg&h=8d408d70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a11f5f6c7b5afb6694d86fd2b87e3f11a8c8bac0","tid":98093,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:59:36.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4932331540b4dcfdf4f4098765e1507b4e9e227","tid":98093,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/145916_25ba3032ad7c5374921604ec89145c48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F145916_25ba3032ad7c5374921604ec89145c48.jpg&h=523a435b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩比三個公會打到好難受，巴絲們幫幫拖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舊圖（兩日前公會Boss）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/145650_3233e009816bd036f22dfb3a79dfcf3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F145650_3233e009816bd036f22dfb3a79dfcf3f.jpg&h=db72cd4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/145706_dac6910379522013078d270cad3ac871.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F145706_dac6910379522013078d270cad3ac871.jpg&h=aa20bbed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/145722_5e861c2e6886460722e404a8901fdd94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F145722_5e861c2e6886460722e404a8901fdd94.jpg&h=23505253&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f16b5e56931831ec69ed63ca18ec2266feb77504","tid":98093,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:00:02.000Z","msg":"一陣搵u"},{"pid":"9f2d0a2a2c2b2a1f22529ffc6263aed402cef107","tid":98093,"uid":21849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"團員幫推！"},{"pid":"4d0b4122b005e520e206efbc057c4b2bf3bb8452","tid":98093,"uid":27821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:43:56.000Z","msg":"可以同盟咩?"},{"pid":"4efcb610cbe4e2cb418ae1075a5c3cbc41652ab5","tid":98093,"uid":9526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:52:27.000Z","msg":"巴打你地打公會王開幾多隊？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05581baf3a6efa9ffde3f06a74e918cbc3814a0","tid":98093,"uid":21849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:42:03.000Z","msg":"班台狗EQ好低"},{"pid":"83d45513059128ea09935590663b10cb46eea364","tid":98093,"uid":64779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6bad7112798131cae283602adbad6fa2a43971d8","tid":98093,"uid":16666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:06:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌好撚嬲有冇巴打都係咁<br />\n琴晚玩完今朝一登入就係咁話我安全碼錯誤<br />\n但係我明明入啱 之後佢就叫我去官網重置安全碼 唔重置就冇得登入<br />\n去到官網點知佢又話send唔到個重置既email <br />\n睇巴哈見到有啲台仔都係咁<br />\nSd左email比客服但係今日一定唔撚覆架啦<br />\n搞到我成日都冇得玩<br />\n屌好撚嬲垃圾代理</blockquote><br />\n暫時自己同身邊朋友都未有呢個問題"},{"pid":"e25c0b5d9d5b95f85323a94b89ef814c53168a4b","tid":98093,"uid":16666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:07:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以同盟咩?</blockquote><br />\n口頭協議姐<br />\n<br />\n到時有事 會支援返大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c1447f9732f6349e25ca9f996df76a8501dbfc","tid":98093,"uid":1348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:11:26.000Z","msg":"想入公會 ,有幾個friend 一齊玩緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60f945de7f49b5a9c39ed50ce9cc8d95841a384","tid":98093,"uid":22331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:11:28.000Z","msg":"係公會果到留左言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b3121cac1343b8224e43a6fee2eee83b17931e","tid":98093,"uid":1348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:14:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想入公會 ,有幾個friend 一齊玩緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTele:@lolap0415"},{"pid":"12d8638d7d23bc09d6